                  </persName>
            . <rs id="t17930911-53-verdict285" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17930911-53-verdict285" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. (Aged 28.)</p>
